This is the terrifying moment a scuba diver looks up from trying to catch a fish to find himself caught in a battle with a shark.

Jason Dmitri was looking for lionfish in the Caribbean Sea when the predator approached, in an encounter which 'scared the cr*p' out of him.

Mr Dimitri, who was carrying a short spear, stabs frantically at the beast as it circles underneath him. It moves in several times to try and snap at him, but he manages to keep it at bay.

