He then swims towards the surface, leaving the shark below. But the beast follows him, and is caught on camera swimming directly towards Mr Dimitri with its jaws wide open.

Aiming the spear downward between his legs, the diver is able again to scare the shark off, and at one point makes contact with the animal's face.

The video, caught on Mr Dimitri's GoPro 3 camera, was uploaded to YouTube last Thursday and has been viewed hundreds of thousands of times.

